Amanda Pays ( born on June 6 , 1959 , in London , England ) is an English actress . Pays is best known for her roles as Theora Jones in the movie and television series Max Headroom and as Christina " Tina " McGee in The Flash . Pays is an interior designer and hosts Fine Living 's The Breathing Room . She married American actor Corbin Bernsen on November 19 , 1988 , with whom she has four sons : Oliver , Henry , Angus , and Finley . She is the niece of former child actress Mandy Miller . She played Sarah in the 1985 miniseries A.D. and narrated the 1988 documentary Computer Dreams . Pays had a guest role in a Season 1 episode of The X - Files , playing the role of Phoebe Green . 